```
$ salt-ssh \* grains.items
host-trusty:
    ----------
    retcode:
        None
    stderr:

    stdout:
        {"biosversion": "VirtualBox", "kernel": "Linux", "domain": "", [snip] 
```

`$ salt-sshh --out grains \* grains.items` does not give better results

By the way, maybe the doc should suggest adding python-msgpack when using salt-ssh (`salt-ssh \* pkg.install python-msgpack`). 
